Sunderland Signs Defender Wes Brown From Manchester Utd.; Fee Undisclosed

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-07-07T13:21:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/sunderland-signs-defender-wes-brown-from-manchester-utd-fee-undisclosed.html
Sunderland said it signed Manchester
United defender  Wes Brown  on a four-year contract.  Sunderland didn’t disclose the transfer fee for the 31-
year-old  England  international in a statement on its website.
News reports say it’s about 1 million pounds ($1.6 million).  John O’Shea and Darron Gibson may also move from Premier
League champion United to Sunderland, according to U.K. reports.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  